reviews.text: Best chain pizza restaurant in Tallahassee! They use real Wisconsin cheese and other high quality ingredients. The team is great and has been mostly the same for many many years, which tells you everything you need to know. The employees are courteous and respectful. I have never received the wrong order or had any issue whatsoever. If you want, great quality pizza, this is the place!

How many stars do I rate them? I mean, it‚Äôs right there in their name! üòÅ Been ordering from Five Star since they opened and have never received bad food.. always a good experience. Nothing fancy but consistent quality is good enough for me.

I order pizza here all the time. They consistently make good pizza and never mess up my order! I've ordered for both delivery and take out and each time the pizza is ready super fast - almost freaky fast. üòâ Every staff member I have interacted with has been friendly and courteous, whether driver or cashier. My husband is a New York pizza snob and this is his favorite place to get pizza. Highly recommend!
The staff were very helpful when I was trying to order. They also helped me get the best deal for my money! Pizza also was the best I‚Äôve had in a while.(and it reheated well!!!)

I have ordered from this place more times than is probably recommended by people who set the standards for # of times one orders from a place..... Anyways... Great food, great pizza and amazing service. I give 5star pizza... Well 5 stars and an explosion emoji!üåüüåüüåüüåüüåüüí•
